#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:1
msgid "Project (`lu_mcp_project`)"
msgstr "Project (`lu_mcp_project`)"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:3
msgid "**7 tools** for Odoo Project task management."
msgstr "Odoo 프로젝트 태스크 관리를 위한 **7가지 도구**입니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:5
msgid "Requires: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `project` app."
msgstr "필요 조건: `lu_mcp_server`, Odoo `project` 앱."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:9
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "개요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:11
msgid ""
"These tools cover the full task lifecycle: browse projects and stages, "
"search tasks, read full task details, create and update tasks, and link "
"Knowledge articles to tasks. Sub-tasks are supported via the `parent_id` "
"parameter on `project_create_task`."
msgstr "이 도구들은 전체 태스크 라이프사이클을 다룹니다: 프로젝트와 스테이지 탐색, 태스크 검색, 전체 태스크 상세 읽기, 생성 및 업데이트, Knowledge 아티클 연결. `project_create_task`의 `parent_id` 파라미터로 서브태스크도 지원합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:17
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "도구"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:19
msgid "`project_list_projects`"
msgstr "`project_list_projects`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:21
msgid "List all active Odoo projects."
msgstr "모든 활성 Odoo 프로젝트를 나열합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "파라미터"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Type"
msgstr "유형"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Required"
msgstr "필수"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Description"
msgstr "설명"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "*(none)*"
msgstr "*(없음)*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:27 ../../mcp/reference/project.md:40
#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:57 ../../mcp/reference/project.md:71
#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:89 ../../mcp/reference/project.md:107
#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:121
msgid "**Example prompt**"
msgstr "**예제 프롬프트**"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:28
msgid "*\"What projects are active in Odoo?\"*"
msgstr "*\"Odoo에서 활성 프로젝트는 어떤 것들이 있나요?\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:32
msgid "`project_list_stages`"
msgstr "`project_list_stages`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:34
msgid "List task stages, optionally filtered to a specific project."
msgstr "태스크 스테이지를 나열하며, 특정 프로젝트로 필터링할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`project_id`"
msgstr "`project_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "integer"
msgstr "integer"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "No"
msgstr "아니요"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Filter stages to a specific project. Omit for all stages."
msgstr "특정 프로젝트의 스테이지만 필터링합니다. 전체 스테이지를 보려면 생략하세요."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:41
msgid "*\"What stages does project #5 use?\"*"
msgstr "*\"프로젝트 #5는 어떤 스테이지를 사용하나요?\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:45
msgid "`project_search_tasks`"
msgstr "`project_search_tasks`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:47
msgid "Search tasks with optional filters."
msgstr "선택적 필터를 사용하여 태스크를 검색합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`query`"
msgstr "`query`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "string"
msgstr "string"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Search keyword in task name or description."
msgstr "태스크 이름 또는 설명에서 검색할 키워드."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Filter by project."
msgstr "프로젝트별 필터링."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`stage_id`"
msgstr "`stage_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Filter by stage."
msgstr "스테이지별 필터링."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`assignee_id`"
msgstr "`assignee_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Filter by assignee (user ID)."
msgstr "담당자별 필터링(사용자 ID)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`limit`"
msgstr "`limit`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Maximum results (default 20, max 80)."
msgstr "최대 결과 수(기본값 20, 최대 80)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:58
msgid "*\"Find all open tasks in the Marketing project assigned to user #3.\"*"
msgstr "*\"마케팅 프로젝트에서 사용자 #3에게 할당된 모든 열린 태스크를 찾으세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:62
msgid "`project_read_task`"
msgstr "`project_read_task`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:64
msgid ""
"Get full details of a task, including description, stage, assignees, "
"deadline, and any linked Knowledge articles."
msgstr "태스크의 전체 상세 정보(설명, 스테이지, 담당자, 마감일, 연결된 Knowledge 아티클 포함)를 가져옵니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`task_id`"
msgstr "`task_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "예"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Numeric task ID."
msgstr "숫자 태스크 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:72
msgid "*\"Show me the details of task #201.\"*"
msgstr "*\"태스크 #201의 상세 정보를 보여주세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:76
msgid "`project_create_task`"
msgstr "`project_create_task`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:78
msgid "Create a new task (or sub-task)."
msgstr "새 태스크(또는 서브태스크)를 생성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`name`"
msgstr "`name`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Task title."
msgstr "태스크 제목."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Project to assign the task to."
msgstr "태스크를 배정할 프로젝트."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`parent_id`"
msgstr "`parent_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Parent task ID — creates a sub-task."
msgstr "부모 태스크 ID — 서브태스크를 생성합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`description`"
msgstr "`description`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Task description (Markdown)."
msgstr "태스크 설명(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "User ID of the assignee."
msgstr "담당자의 사용자 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`deadline`"
msgstr "`deadline`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Deadline date (`YYYY-MM-DD`)."
msgstr "마감일(`YYYY-MM-DD`)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:90
msgid ""
"*\"Create a task 'Prepare Q3 report' in project #5 assigned to user #8, "
"due 2026-09-30.\"*"
msgstr "*\"프로젝트 #5에서 'Q3 보고서 준비' 태스크를 생성하고, 사용자 #8에게 할당하며, 마감일을 2026-09-30으로 설정하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:94
msgid "`project_update_task`"
msgstr "`project_update_task`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:96
msgid "Update an existing task."
msgstr "기존 태스크를 업데이트합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Task ID to update."
msgstr "업데이트할 태스크 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "New task title."
msgstr "새 태스크 제목."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Move to a different stage."
msgstr "다른 스테이지로 이동."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Change the assignee."
msgstr "담당자 변경."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "New deadline (`YYYY-MM-DD`)."
msgstr "새 마감일(`YYYY-MM-DD`)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "New description (Markdown)."
msgstr "새 설명(Markdown)."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:108
msgid "*\"Move task #201 to the 'Done' stage.\"*"
msgstr "*\"태스크 #201을 'Done' 스테이지로 이동하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:112
msgid "`project_link_knowledge_article`"
msgstr "`project_link_knowledge_article`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:114
msgid ""
"Link a Knowledge article to a task. Requires the Odoo `knowledge` app to "
"be installed."
msgstr "태스크에 Knowledge 아티클을 연결합니다. Odoo `knowledge` 앱이 설치되어 있어야 합니다."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Task ID."
msgstr "태스크 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "`article_id`"
msgstr "`article_id`"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md
msgid "Knowledge article ID to link."
msgstr "연결할 Knowledge 아티클 ID."

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:122
msgid "*\"Link Knowledge article #55 to task #201.\"*"
msgstr "*\"Knowledge 아티클 #55를 태스크 #201에 연결하세요.\"*"

#: ../../mcp/reference/project.md:125
msgid ""
"This tool is only registered when the `knowledge` Odoo app is installed. "
"If Knowledge is not installed, the tool will not appear in `tools/list`."
msgstr "이 도구는 Odoo `knowledge` 앱이 설치된 경우에만 등록됩니다. Knowledge가 설치되지 않은 경우 `tools/list`에 표시되지 않습니다."
